Tested 31.07.2014 on RoundCube 1.0.1
Tested 30.08.2014 on RoundCube 1.0.2
Tested 23.03.2015 on Roundcube 1.0.3
Tested 23.03.2015 on Roundcube 1.1.0 (UP version to 0.2.4)

